<item>
            <title>[LU-11293] Error: Unable to create resource &apos;ocf:lustre:Lustre&apos;, it is not installed on this system</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11293</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Not sure if this resource is managed by WC or by Cluster Labs, but I can&apos;t seem to find any information on cluster labs regarding it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
Error: Unable to create resource &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;ocf:lustre:Lustre&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, it is not installed on &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; system&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I can&apos;t seem to find the resource on clusterlabs github, but I&apos;m trying to add a resource for ldiskfs as per the[Lustre.org description|&lt;a href=&quot;http://wiki.lustre.org/Creating_Pacemaker_Resources_for_Lustre_Storage_Services&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://wiki.lustre.org/Creating_Pacemaker_Resources_for_Lustre_Storage_Services&lt;/a&gt;]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Is it possible that you&apos;d have some information as to what I can do to install the resource? Or should I speak with Cluster Labs?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
